Gunthers, Soundwave was also supposed to accompany Havotron, 
so i'm going to post for him following.

--- Soundwave / Bonecrusher ---

Bonecrusher leaps into flight, following his fellow Constructicons, 
and Havotron

Soundwave follows Bonecrusher, who is probably the last to leave. 
He flies after the bots, a single thought racing in his quick him, 
<Megatron?!?> He wished to join his original leader.
